    },
    "content": {
        "rendered": "<h2>Basic Setup</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Create a new Field Group</li>\n<li>Add an Accordion field</li>\n<li>Configure basic settings:\n<ul>\n<li>Set a clear section title</li>\n<li>Choose if it should be open by default</li>\n<li>Decide if multiple sections can be open</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>Common Use Cases</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Organizing Content Sections\n<ul>\n<li>Group related fields together</li>\n<li>Use clear section names</li>\n<li>Consider the editing workflow</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Creating Form Sections\n<ul>\n<li>Basic Information</li>\n<li>Detailed Content</li>\n<li>Settings/Configuration</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>Tips</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Keep section names concise but descriptive</li>\n<li>Don&#8217;t nest accordions too deeply</li>\n<li>Consider using endpoints to create clear breaks</li>\n<li>Group related fields logically</li>\n</ul>\n",
